Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points

Interface FillingArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of numeric coordinates that are encapsulated in the object of the Point class.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Filling<Array<Point<T>>>, FillingArray<Point<T>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FillingArrayPointsRandomDoubleNumbers, FillingArrayPointsRandomIntegerNumbers, FillingArrayPointsReadDoubleNumbers, FillingArrayPointsReadIntegerNumbers
    public interface FillingArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>
extends FillingArray<Point<T>>
    The interface declares a contract to implement the filling of an objects of Array and classical array objects of the Point class with coordinates of a numerical type.

    Created by Konstantin Lugowoy on 27-Jan-18.

    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Konstantin Lugowoy
